_sText:
When running on servers this map is designed for no awp and autosnipers.


DE_VENITIAN_SUN_BETA

A CounterStrike.Source Map by La Gare

Thanks for downloading my first map! Hope you like!

The .bsp and the .nav file go in the following directory

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\"YOUR STEAM ID/NAME"\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

and the .cache file goes in the soundcache folder

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\"YOUR STEAM ID/NAME"\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps\soundcache

When you've extracted them to their correct directories you're ready to go!

Oh! And a little tip, the boat on the map...like any boat on cs.s has some issues, drive slowly at first!
The steering wheel is the ignition. It's set to start on touch AND on use so either walk into the 
steering wheel or press e on it. It does sometimes have problems, but be persistant it will start!

Enjoy! And thanks again for downloading!


La Gare
